    <measure>The volume of compensated blood loss with the formula: [TBV x (initial hematocrit - final hematocrit ) + number of transfused RBC unit] with TBV=Total Blood Volume and RBC= red blood cell (1 RBC unit = 500 ml with hematocrit=30%).</measure>
