  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Signature of the consent form

          -  Patients with hepatic lesion needing a major hepatectomy (≥ 3 hepatic segments)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Absence of signature of the consent form

          -  Patient with cirrhosis

          -  Minor hepatectomy (&lt; 3 hepatic segments)

          -  Hepatectomy associated with vascular resection

          -  Contraindication of tranexamic acid : history of arterial or venous thrombosis ,
             disseminated intravascular coagulation, severe renal insufficiency, history of
             epilepsies , intrathecal or intraventricular injection

          -  Pregnant or lactation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
